name: Dipped Studded Teardrop Necklace
description:
This sweet teardrop shaped empty bezel necklace is made of Copper and dipped in Gold tone powdercoat, with fantastic little tube set Cubic Zirconia.

Teardrop shape is approx. 1"x1".

Strung on a 16" sterling silver chain with handmade hook and eye style clasp.

name: Dipped O Earring
description:
These delicious little earrings are made of Brass and dipped in Gold tone powdercoat, with sterling silver ear posts.

Approx. .25" squared.

name: Dipped Studded Teardrop Earrings
description:
Be bold and non-conformist, yet maintain the class and elegance of the traditional stud earring in these sweet little studded teardrops -- made of Copper and dipped in Gold tone powdercoat, with fantastic little tube set Cubic Zirconia! Perfect little companion pieces to set off any favorite little black dress!

Teardrop shape is approx. 1"x1". Sterling silver ear posts.

name: Bird Dangle Earrings
description:
Stand out in these adorable dangling bird earrings! Completely hand fabricated from sterling silver wires and brass sheet metal. 

Bold enough to make a statement, but lightweight enough to wear every day!

Hang at roughly 2.5".

name: Midnight Affliction Earrings
description:
Make heads turn in these gorgeous little bling studded teardrops!  Entirely handmade, these stunning little jewels reference empty bezels and organic growth. 

Perfectly sized for everyday wear, but bold enough for any sophisticated night out - a fabulous little bit of sparkle for that little black dress! 

Made from copper, tastefully adorned with four white cubic zirconia, and finished with a variable blue patina.
 
Also available with SI quality white diamonds.
